Yoshimoto's father was Imagawa Ujichika (1473-1526).  Imagawa 
Yoshimoto was Ujichika's third son. Ujizane (1538-1614) was the son 
of Imagawa Yoshimoto and Sadae-in (a daughter of Takeda Nobutora).
